snippet.title: FJX Imperium Sniper Reveal | Call of Duty: Modern Warfare II & Warzone 2.0
snippet.description:
We invited FaZeDirty for a surprise Season 03 playtest 😯

What he didn't know was an old friend would be joining him. The FJX Imperium Sniper drops with Season 03 on April 12 🎯

Follow #CallofDuty for the latest intel:
